      "bullets": [
        "Generative AI and voice cloning scale highly convincing social engineering, rendering traditional text-based phishing indicators obsolete.",
        "Deepfakes and LLMs automate spear-phishing, enabling attackers to bypass biometric verification and MFA via real-time synthesis.",
        "Defense requires transitioning from passive detection to zero-trust verification, cryptographic signatures, and out-of-band channels."
      ]
    },
