      "bullets": [
        "Lobste.rs archives offer deep, peer-reviewed engineering insights on systems design, language pragmatics, and historical software architecture decisions.",
        "The invite-only moderation model preserves high signal-to-noise, safeguarding highly technical critiques, performance optimizations, and obscure bug post-mortems.",
        "Mining older threads uncovers production-tested database trade-offs, systems programming wisdom, and pragmatic architectural retrospectives from senior practitioners."
