      "author": "ABGEO",
      "published": "2026-06-18T06:36:39Z",
      "bullets": [
        "Implement OAuth 2.0 Device Authorization Grant (RFC 8628) to authenticate CLI tools securely using browser-based identity providers.",
        "Store session tokens in native OS credential managers like macOS Keychain or Linux Secret Service instead of plaintext files.",
        "Replace long-lived static API keys with short-lived tokens and OIDC federation to minimize the blast radius of compromised credentials."
      ]
    },
