      "bullets": [
        "K8s interviews heavily prioritize real-world Day-2 operations, testing deep troubleshooting of etcd, CoreDNS bottlenecks, and CNI networking failures over basic YAML.",
        "Employers value GitOps automation using ArgoCD or Flux and secure secret management with HashiCorp Vault over manual kubectl deployments.",
        "Technical loops focus on cost-efficiency tools like Karpenter alongside architectural decisions on when to bypass Kubernetes for simpler ECS setups."
      ]
